As for other guild walking over each other for spawns, it happens to us all, its up to the officers  to clear up the problem and act mature not for us to come bitch on the board where nothing will get done. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ukaerilabuffaholic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kaerila Buffaholic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Regular Poster</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/11/02 6:51:54 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=810.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sad Grumblings</span><hr size=1> Kiv!!!<br>
<br>
I miss you silly man <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    <br>
